@baseUrl = https://papi-sundaygap.netlify.app

### Sanity check - expect HTTP 405 Method Not Allowed
GET {{baseUrl}}/.netlify/functions/send-sms

### Send a test reminder - expect 200 {success, sid} or 4xx {error}
POST {{baseUrl}}/.netlify/functions/send-sms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "+15555550100",
  "message": "Test: Papi care reminder working."
}
